Documentation on the Wise Club
==============================

The Wise Person's Club is a minor guild, giving qualifying
players a few emotes and a pin to wear. The join room is
located at /d/Krynn/solace/new_village/wise_club.c.
Players may leave the club at any time, with a function for
leaving within the pin. The pin is autoloading, and is located
in /d/Krynn/solace/new_village/obj/wise_object.c.

Requirements to join the club:
The player must be 100 days old, in game age.

